This torrent marked my 225th Fame-Girls upload. Would have been more, but I was banned back in Dec of 2010, and those previous FG uploads were deleted. It was a misunderstanding, and the ban was reversed. 1 year, 1 month, 15 days later, here we are.

I sent an email to the wmi site owner, and he said he will continue to do the blog and previews. So if you guys still need a fix, there is always that.

Anyways, have fun all. Peace. Love ya guys.
